sequenceDiagram
  participant UI as Web UI
  participant API as Control Abstraction
  participant AD as SDR Adapter (WASM or JS)
  participant DEV as SDR Device (WebUSB)

  UI->>API: Build high-level request (JSON)
  API->>AD: Dispatch request
  AD->>DEV: Send device-specific command(s)
  DEV-->>AD: Reply / status
  AD-->>API: Normalize response
  API-->>UI: Update state / UI